You do stuff in different factions in the
games, you get a little

00:15:52.060 --> 00:15:55.390
reputation here.
You gain a bit of reputation there.

00:15:55.390 --> 00:15:58.360
You're more welcome in the city.
You get better prices in that city.

00:15:58.360 --> 00:16:01.490
At the same time, there's player versus player,
if you want to PvP

00:16:01.490 --> 00:16:05.870
serve, beat other people up and get different
items.

00:16:05.870 --> 00:16:09.230
At the same time, there's gear.
There's this tantalizing random element, every

00:16:09.230 --> 00:16:12.600
time you attack a morph,
it's going to drop something with a chance

00:16:12.600 --> 00:16:18.990
of it being really, really, really awesome.
And this is an amazing book, it was perfected

00:16:18.990 --> 00:16:21.610
[INAUDIBLE] this in the
Diablo series of games.

00:16:21.610 --> 00:16:24.770
And whole Warcraft.
This is the very, very powerful incentive

00:16:24.770 --> 00:16:30.180
to people to just kill that
next bore and see if it happens to drop a

00:16:30.180 --> 00:16:31.700
