00:30:37.559 --> 00:30:41.940
because [INAUDIBLE] examples of times when
you just completely fail

00:30:41.940 --> 00:30:46.509
like [INAUDIBLE] that but I think there's
another thing as well as not

00:30:46.509 --> 00:30:48.500
yet succeeding, which is also like a human
desire to beat other people.

00:30:48.500 --> 00:30:50.029
And if you're playing on say like Halo or
something like that, you play

00:30:50.029 --> 00:30:54.710
that because like you want to defeat other
people and show superiority

00:30:54.710 --> 00:30:58.549
over them.
I think that's another like equally important

00:30:58.549 --> 00:31:00.679
thought as not yet
succeeding.

00:31:00.679 --> 00:31:04.529
TOM CHATFIELD: Yeah, in terms of not -- in
